    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>I have a controller action called "professionalExperiences", with a relative view script having "professionalExperiences.phtml" as a file name, placed in the correct view folder.</p>

<p>On my local server (Mac OS X with Apache2) everything works: with small caps only, and with camelCaps. On the production server (linux with Apache2), with camelCaps I get the error reported below, while will small caps only it works fine.</p>

<p>==========================================================================================</p>

<h1>Fatal error: Uncaught exception 'Zend_View_Exception' with message 'script 'account/professionalexperiences.phtml' not found in path (./application/frontend/views/scripts/)' in /home/15219/domains/fresworks.com/html/everydoby/library/Zend/View/Abstract.php:856 Stack trace: #0 /home/15219/domains/fresworks.com/html/everydoby/library/Zend/View/Abstract.php(764): Zend_View_Abstract-&gt;_script('account/profess...') #1 /home/15219/domains/fresworks.com/html/everydoby/library/Zend/Controller/Action/Helper/ViewRenderer.php(742): Zend_View_Abstract-&gt;render('account/profess...') #2 /home/15219/domains/fresworks.com/html/everydoby/library/Zend/Controller/Action/Helper/ViewRenderer.php(763): Zend_Controller_Action_Helper_ViewRenderer-&gt;renderScript('account/profess...', NULL) #3 /home/15219/domains/fresworks.com/html/everydoby/library/Zend/Controller/Action/Helper/ViewRenderer.php(810): Zend_Controller_Action_Helper_ViewRenderer-&gt;render() #4 /home/15219/domains/fresworks.com/html/everydoby/library/Zend/Controller/Action/HelperBroker.ph in /home/15219/domains/fresworks.com/html/everydoby/library/Zend/View/Abstract.php on line 856</h1>

<p>I found out that correcting the filename and writing it in SMALL CAPS ONLY makes the scritp work again.
